metadata.name: ONCHAIN AUSTRALIA
metadata.created_by: boot x Clouted x Rowdy x zee
metadata.description: ONCHAIN AUSTRALIA is a fully decentralised community that champions the idea of connectivity between Australian's in Web3. We are an all-inclusive society, that aims to provide value to our collective at NO COST. Whomever you are, whatever your message, we want to build Australia's tomorrow with you today.
